TANY 50th Annual Conference & Membership Meeting


        Watkins Glen, NY
        9/25/2017 - 9/27/2017
    

For 85 years, the Trucking Association of New York (TANY) (formerly the New York State Motor Truck Association) a non-profit trade group, has represented the trucking industry in New York, advocating for the industry at the local, state and federal levels. 




